<i>Previously on</i> This Is Us...

00:01.766 --> 00:02.796
You know, when I was a kid,

00:02.820 --> 00:04.414
I was obsessed with <i>Star Wars.</i>

00:04.493 --> 00:06.027
Luke, Vader,

00:06.117 --> 00:07.906
Leia, Obi-Wan.

00:09.851 --> 00:11.750
(SIGHS) They were on the inside.

00:12.277 --> 00:13.878
Action!

00:13.903 --> 00:15.404
(GROANS)

00:16.421 --> 00:17.703
KATE: <i>Kev's in rehab.</i>

00:17.728 --> 00:19.500
I let Kevin get sent to rehab.

00:19.525 --> 00:21.265
BARBARA: <i>You know what,
I'm very proud of you, Kevin,</i>

00:21.290 --> 00:23.632
but in here is in here, but out there,

00:23.657 --> 00:26.671
- just takes one second to slip up.
- Yeah.

00:27.149 --> 00:29.150
My foster dad helped me with that.

00:29.427 --> 00:31.528
SHAUNA: <i>And if you want to know
what's best for her,</i>

00:31.562 --> 00:33.500
it's me, and the second
I get out of here,

00:33.525 --> 00:34.828
I'm coming back for her.

00:34.853 --> 00:36.254
Hey, girl.

00:38.327 --> 00:39.921
BETH: <i>I'm gonna miss her.</i>

00:40.642 --> 00:41.921
RANDALL: <i>Me, too.</i>

00:44.289 --> 00:45.507
- (PHONE RINGS)
- Hello.

00:50.696 --> 00:55.300
♪ <i>As around the sun the Earth</i>
<i>knows she's revolving</i> ♪

00:56.287 --> 00:58.555
♪ <i>And the rosebuds know to bloom...</i> ♪

00:58.589 --> 01:00.557
- Oh-ho-ho!
- (REBECCA WHOOPING)

01:00.591 --> 01:01.781
- JACK: Another...
- (REBECCA LAUGHS)

01:01.806 --> 01:05.062
- five-seven split by my wife.
- (REBECCA WHOOPS)

01:05.504 --> 01:09.125
I love it. My husband knows
all the bowling lingo.

01:09.467 --> 01:10.796
JACK: (LAUGHS) Wow.

01:10.821 --> 01:13.492
This is the best first anniversary ever.

01:13.829 --> 01:15.320
- Hey, babe?
- Mm-hmm?

01:15.421 --> 01:16.742
Are you ready for your gift?

01:16.946 --> 01:18.046
Mm-hmm.

01:18.609 --> 01:21.144
♪ <i>Just as all is born is new</i> ♪

01:21.178 --> 01:23.132
♪ <i>Do know what I say is true</i> ♪

01:23.157 --> 01:25.437
- ♪ <i>That I'll be loving you always</i> ♪
- Oh.

01:26.617 --> 01:28.054
♪ <i>Until the...</i> ♪

01:28.834 --> 01:31.414
Because you're always scribbling
on all those scraps of paper,

01:31.439 --> 01:34.101
I started collecting them
and then I had them bound.

01:34.359 --> 01:35.959
- Uh-huh. (JACK LAUGHS)
- Is it stupid?

01:35.993 --> 01:37.601
'Cause in my mind, when
I was doing it, - What?

01:37.626 --> 01:38.851
it was really romantic.

01:38.876 --> 01:43.867
Rebecca, th-this is
the most romantic gift ever.

01:43.974 --> 01:45.523
Oh, I love you.

01:47.039 --> 01:48.898
MAN (OVER P.A.): <i>Mr. and Mrs. Pearson,</i>

01:48.953 --> 01:51.029
please make your way to lane 30

01:51.054 --> 01:52.956
<i>for a very special dance.</i>

01:52.991 --> 01:54.525
- (APPLAUSE)
- (REBECCA GIGGLES)

01:55.226 --> 01:56.427
(JACK LAUGHS)

01:56.851 --> 01:59.653
♪ <i>As around the sun the Earth knows...</i> ♪

02:00.367 --> 02:01.732
Holy crap, Jack.

02:01.945 --> 02:03.265
Happy anniversary.

02:03.546 --> 02:05.773
♪ <i>...to bloom in early May</i> ♪

02:06.828 --> 02:08.895
♪ <i>Just as hate knows love's the cure</i> ♪

02:08.930 --> 02:11.298
♪ <i>You can rest your mind assure</i> ♪

02:11.687 --> 02:15.320
♪ <i>That I'll be loving you always...</i> ♪

02:16.320 --> 02:19.054
- To four years.
- Mm. To four years.

02:20.695 --> 02:22.109
Do you want your gift?

02:22.610 --> 02:25.179
- Yeah. (LAUGHS)
- Yeah? It's time?

02:25.213 --> 02:26.796
All right.

02:27.451 --> 02:29.920
(SINGSONGY): I've been
waiting to give this to you.

02:29.945 --> 02:31.951
- Oh, wow.
- Open it.

02:32.179 --> 02:33.718
- (CHUCKLES) Silly.
- ♪ <i>I'll be loving you</i> ♪

02:33.823 --> 02:35.857
- ♪ <i>Always</i> ♪
- ♪ <i>Until the rainbow...</i> ♪

02:36.164 --> 02:37.803
Because you're always talking about

02:37.828 --> 02:39.920
how the new guys on the job
sites take your hammer.

02:39.945 --> 02:41.389
Oh. That is beautiful.

02:41.414 --> 02:43.030
Babe, I love it.

02:43.257 --> 02:44.406
♪ <i>Always</i> ♪

02:44.431 --> 02:47.859
♪ <i>Until the dolphin flies
and parrots live at sea</i> ♪

02:47.884 --> 02:49.062
♪ <i>Always</i> ♪

02:49.095 --> 02:51.920
♪ <i>Until the earth just for
the sun denies itself</i> ♪

02:51.945 --> 02:53.968
I love this piano so much.

02:53.993 --> 02:57.707
♪ <i>Until dear Mother Nature
says her work is through</i> ♪

02:58.079 --> 03:01.489
♪ <i>Until the day that you
are me and I am you...</i> ♪

03:03.085 --> 03:04.898
- (WHISPERS): Jack.
- (JACK SNORTS)

03:07.710 --> 03:09.101
Happy anniversary.

03:09.171 --> 03:11.617
Oh, happy anniversary, babe.

03:11.828 --> 03:13.227
- Mm.
- Hey.

03:13.261 --> 03:15.262
(JACK SNIFFS, SIGHS)

03:17.398 --> 03:19.066
Can you promise me there aren't any

03:19.100 --> 03:21.568
big grand gestures planned this morning?

03:21.812 --> 03:23.704
No. No, not this year.

03:24.757 --> 03:27.074
Okay. 'Cause you promised,
and I didn't get you anything.

03:27.108 --> 03:29.148
Oh, I know. I know.

03:32.000 --> 03:33.947
Patrick Swayze's not gonna pop out

03:33.982 --> 03:36.046
- of our closet, is he?
- (LAUGHS)

03:36.071 --> 03:38.719
- It's always Swayze with you.
- I don't know.

03:38.753 --> 03:41.755
- Sorry.
- No. No big grand gestures.

03:42.445 --> 03:43.757
No gifts.

03:43.898 --> 03:45.659
No guilt.

03:45.693 --> 03:48.773
That's what you asked for
this year, and I'm obeying.

03:49.140 --> 03:50.287
Thank you.

03:50.312 --> 03:52.320
We'll get the kids to bed early.

03:52.453 --> 03:54.467
Say around...

03:54.499 --> 03:56.810
- 8:30 Eastern Standard Time.
- Yeah.

03:56.835 --> 03:59.106
And then we'll be right back here in bed

03:59.140 --> 04:02.453
- watching <i>The Commish</i> finale.
- Yes. Thank you.

04:02.478 --> 04:05.112
- That's all I want, just one year.
- Mm-hmm.

04:05.250 --> 04:08.449
My two favourite guys:
you and The Commish.

04:09.568 --> 04:10.687
Yeah.

04:16.858 --> 04:18.062
♪

