21:02.566 --> 21:04.546
♪ <i>All that you can dream</i> ♪

21:05.273 --> 21:08.137
♪ <i>I can make come true</i> ♪

21:08.398 --> 21:14.009
♪ <i>I will help you read</i>
<i>your favorite bedtime story</i> ♪

21:14.044 --> 21:18.273
♪ <i>I'm the one that belongs,</i>
<i>right, never wrong for you</i> ♪

